### ============================================================================
### LLM-AGENT-API-001 | 에이전트 실행 상태 조회
### Markdown source: docs/03_Specifications/03_LLM/api/LLM_API_SPEC.md
### Endpoint: GET /api/chat/{repo_id}/runs/{run_id}
### 관련 기능 ID: LLM-AGENT-B-201, LLM-AGENT-B-202, LLM-AGENT-B-203,
### LLM-AGENT-B-204
### 상태: 구현 완료
### ============================================================================
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000
@accessToken = replace-me
@repoId = 3f7cc46e-d954-83ab-9f12-013b0c9d2a1e
@runId = replace-me-run-id

GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/{{repoId}}/runs/{{runId}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 200 OK
### {"code":200,"message":"success","data":{"runId":"...","sessionId":"...","status":"running","currentNode":"worker_started","state":{"userQuery":"로그인 어딧음?","rewrittenQuery":"login signin auth authentication","accessPlan":{"selectedWorkers":["search","grep"],"allowedPaths":["backend/app"]},"securityResult":{"allowed":true,"parallelGroups":[["search"],["grep"]]},"workerResultCount":2,"compactContextReady":false,"stateKeys":["user_query","rewritten_query","access_plan","security_result","worker_results"]},"durations":{},"finalAnswer":null,"error":null}}
### status: queued | running | streaming | completed | failed | cancelled
### status/evidence/cancel은 run registry에 보존된 RunRecord를 기준으로 응답한다.

### [오류] 없는 run
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/chat/{{repoId}}/runs/missing-run
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
Accept: application/json

### 401 UNAUTHORIZED / 404 LLM_RUN_NOT_FOUND
### {"detail":"Run not found"}
